Package FestivalPlanner.GUI.AgendaGUI

Contains classes related to elements drawn on screen, such as objects used by JavaFX.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgendaCanvas
    Contains all methods that draw an Agenda to a canvas.
    AgendaModule
    Responsible for placing everything in the correct place in the Agenda GUI and making sure all the buttons work.
    ArtistAndPodiumEditorGUI
    Contains all elements and methods seen in used in the artist and podium creation/removal window.
    ShowEditorGUI
    Contains all elements and methods seen and used in the edit window of the GUI.
    ShowRectangle2D
    Responsible for the rectangles representing shows on the canvas.
